\c 50
\50Zvanzi naJehovha, "Ruripiko rugwaro rwokuramba mai venyu, rwandakavaramba narwo? Kana ndakakutengesai kuna ani vandakanga ndine chikwerete navo here? Tarirai makatengeswa nokuda kwezvakaipa zvenyu, mai venyu vakarambwa nokuda kwokudarika kwenyu. 2 Ndakashaireiko munhu pakusvika kwangu? Ndakashaireiko akapindura pakudana kwangu? Ko ruoko rwangu rwatongopfupiswa kuti rukoniwe kudzikinura here? Handine simba rokurwira here? Tarirai, ndinopwisa gungwa kana ndichirituka, nzizi ndinodziita renje; hove dzadzo dzinonhuwa, nokuti hadzine mvura, dzinofa nenyota. 3 Denga rose ndinorifukidza nokusviba, chifukidziro charo ndinochiita makudza."
\s Muranda waJehovha
\p
\v 4 Ishe Jehovha akandipa rurimi rwavakadzidziswa, kuti ndizive kusimbisa vakaneta namashoko; anondimutsa mangwanani ose, anomutsa nzeve dzangu kuti ndinzwe savanodzidziswa.
\v 5 Ishe Jehovha akadziura nzeve dzangu, handina kuramba kana kudzokera shure.
\p
\v 6 Ndakarinzira varovi musana wangu, namatama angu kuna vakataura ndebvu dzangu; handina kuvanza chiso changu pakunyadziswa nokupfirwa mate.
\v 7 Nokuti Ishe Jehovha achandibatsira, naizvozvo handina kunyadziswa; naizvozvo ndakaita chiso changu sebwe romusarasara, ndinoziva kuti handinganyadziswi.
\v 8 Anondiruramisira ari pedyo; ndiani acharwa neni? Ngatisimukei pamwechete, ndiani mudzivisi wangu? Ngaaswedere kwandiri.
\v 9 Tarirai, Ishe, Jehovha achandibatsira; ndiani angandipa mhosva? Tarirai, avo vose vachasakara senguo; vachadyiwa nezvipfunho.
\p
\v 10 Ndianiko aripo pakati penyu anotya Jehovha, anoteerera izwi romuranda wake? Anofamba murima, asina chiedza, ngaavimbe nezita raJehovha, asendame kuna Mwari wake. " Tarirai, imi mose, munobatidza moto, munozvisunga zviuno nezvitsiga; fambai mumurazvo womoto wenyu, napakati pezvitsiga zvamakabatidza. Muchapiwa izvozvo noruoko rwangu, muchavata pasi muchitambudzika.
